trans-unit.target: CTRL / COMMAND + LEFT ：移至前一天。

trans-unit.source: DOWN/RIGHT: Move focus to the next item.
trans-unit.target: DOWN / RIGHT ：将焦点移到下一个项目。

trans-unit.target: DOWN / RIGHT ：将焦点移到下一个选项卡。如果在最后一个选项卡上，则将焦点移至第一个选项卡。短暂延迟后激活焦点标签。

trans-unit.source: DOWN/RIGHT: Select the next item.
trans-unit.target: DOWN / RIGHT ：选择下一个项目。

trans-unit.source: DOWN: Decrement the value by one step.
trans-unit.target: DOWN ：将值递减一步。

trans-unit.source: DOWN: Move focus to the next item. If on last item, move focus to the input. If on the input, move focus to the first item.
trans-unit.target: DOWN ：将焦点移到下一个项目。如果在最后一项上，则将焦点移至输入。如果在输入上，则将焦点移到第一项。

trans-unit.source: DOWN: Move focus to the next menu item.
trans-unit.target: DOWN ：将焦点移到下一个菜单项。

trans-unit.source: END/PAGE DOWN: Move focus to the last item.
trans-unit.target: END / PAGE DOWN ：将焦点移到最后一项。

trans-unit.source: END/PAGE DOWN: Select the last item.
trans-unit.target: END / PAGE DOWN ：选择最后一项。

trans-unit.source: END: Move focus to the last header.
trans-unit.target: END ：将焦点移到最后一个标题。

trans-unit.source: END: Move focus to the last tab. Activate focused tab after a short delay.
trans-unit.target: END ：将焦点移至最后一个标签。短暂延迟后激活焦点标签。

trans-unit.source: ENTER/SPACE: Invoke the focused menu item's action, which may be opening a submenu.
trans-unit.target: ENTER / SPACE ：调用焦点菜单项的操作，这可能正在打开子菜单。

trans-unit.source: ENTER/SPACE: Select the currently focused item and close the menu.
trans-unit.target: ENTER / SPACE ：选择当前关注的项目并关闭菜单。

trans-unit.source: ENTER: Activate or toggle panel associated with focused tab.
trans-unit.target: ENTER ：激活或切换与焦点选项卡关联的面板。

trans-unit.source: ENTER: Select the currently focused item and close the menu.
trans-unit.target: ENTER ：选择当前关注的项目并关闭菜单。

trans-unit.source: ENTER: Select the focused date.
trans-unit.target: ENTER ：选择重点日期。

trans-unit.source: ESCAPE: Close the current submenu and move focus to the parent menu item. If not in a submenu, do nothing.
trans-unit.target: ESCAPE ：关闭当前子菜单，然后将焦点移到父菜单项。如果不在子菜单中，则什么也不做。

trans-unit.source: ESCAPE: Close the datepicker without selection.
trans-unit.target: ESCAPE ：不选择就关闭日期选择器。

trans-unit.source: ESCAPE: Close the menu.
trans-unit.target: ESCAPE ：关闭菜单。

trans-unit.source: ESCAPE: Close the tooltip.
trans-unit.target: ESCAPE ：关闭工具提示。

trans-unit.source: HOME/PAGE UP: Move focus to the first item.
trans-unit.target: HOME / PAGE UP ：将焦点移到第一项。

trans-unit.source: HOME/PAGE UP: Select the first item.
trans-unit.target: HOME / PAGE UP ：选择第一项。

trans-unit.source: HOME: Move focus to the first header.
trans-unit.target: HOME ：将焦点移到第一个标题。

trans-unit.source: HOME: Move focus to the first tab. Activate focused tab after a short delay.
trans-unit.target: HOME ：将焦点移到第一个选项卡。短暂延迟后激活焦点标签。

trans-unit.source: LEFT: Close the current submenu and move focus to the parent menu item. If not in a submenu, do nothing.
trans-unit.target: LEFT ：关闭当前子菜单并将焦点移到父菜单项。如果不在子菜单中，则什么也不做。

trans-unit.source: PAGE DOWN: Decrement the value by one page.
trans-unit.target: PAGE DOWN ：将值减少一页。

trans-unit.source: PAGE DOWN: Move to the next month.
trans-unit.target: PAGE DOWN ：移至下个月。

trans-unit.source: PAGE UP/PAGE DOWN: Scroll through a page of items (based on height of menu). It's generally a bad idea to display so many items that users need to page.
trans-unit.target: PAGE UP / PAGE DOWN ：滚动浏览项目页面（基于菜单的高度）。显示太多用户需要分页的项目通常是一个坏主意。

trans-unit.source: PAGE UP: Increment the value by one page.
trans-unit.target: PAGE UP ：将值增加一页。

trans-unit.source: PAGE UP: Move to the previous month.
trans-unit.target: PAGE UP ：移至上个月。

trans-unit.source: RIGHT: Open the submenu, if available.
trans-unit.target: RIGHT ：打开子菜单（如果有）。

trans-unit.source: SPACE/ENTER: Activate panel associated with focused header.
trans-unit.target: SPACE / ENTER ：激活与焦点标题关联的面板。

trans-unit.source: SPACE: Activate panel associated with focused tab.
trans-unit.target: SPACE ：激活与焦点选项卡关联的面板。

trans-unit.source: SPACE: Open the menu.
trans-unit.target: SPACE ：打开菜单。

trans-unit.source: TAB: Select the currently focused item, close the menu, and move focus to the next focusable element.
trans-unit.target: TAB ：选择当前关注的项目，关闭菜单，然后将焦点移到下一个可聚焦的元素。

trans-unit.source: UP/DOWN: Open the menu, if the minLength has been met.
trans-unit.target: UP / DOWN ：打开菜单，如果 minLength 已经达到。

trans-unit.source: UP/LEFT: Move focus to the previous header. If on first header, moves focus to last header.
trans-unit.target: UP / LEFT ：将焦点移到上一个标题。如果在第一个标题上，则将焦点移到最后一个标题。

trans-unit.source: UP/LEFT: Move focus to the previous item.
trans-unit.target: UP / LEFT ：将焦点移到上一个项目。

trans-unit.source: UP/LEFT: Move focus to the previous tab. If on first tab, moves focus to last tab. Activate focused tab after a short delay.
trans-unit.target: UP / LEFT ：将焦点移到上一个选项卡。如果在第一个选项卡上，则将焦点移至最后一个选项卡。短暂延迟后激活焦点标签。

trans-unit.source: UP/LEFT: Select the previous item.
trans-unit.target: UP / LEFT ：选择上一项。

trans-unit.source: UP: Increment the value by one step.
trans-unit.target: UP ：将值增加一级。

trans-unit.source: UP: Move focus to the previous item. If on first item, move focus to the input. If on the input, move focus to last item.
trans-unit.target: UP ：将焦点移到上一个项目。如果在第一项上，则将焦点移至输入。如果在输入上，则将焦点移到最后一项。

trans-unit.source: UP: Move focus to the previous menu item.
trans-unit.target: UP ：将焦点移到上一个菜单项。

trans-unit.target: [1] ：要添加到日期的单元格的CSS类名称，或默认表示形式的 ""

trans-unit.source: [2]: an optional popup tooltip for this date

trans-unit.source: controlgroupLabel: Any elements matching the selector for this will be wrapped in a span with the ui-controlgroup-label-contents class.
trans-unit.target: controlgroupLabel ：与此选择器匹配的任何元素都将使用 ui-controlgroup-label-contents 类包装在一个范围中。

trans-unit.source: element: the DOM element this instance was created on
trans-unit.target: element ：创建此实例的DOM元素

trans-unit.source: jQuery.effects.createPlaceholder() will create a placeholder with the same display, position, dimensions, and margins as the original element. The placeholder is inserted into the DOM as the next sibling of the original element. When the animation is complete, jQuery.effects.removePlaceholder() should be used to remove the inserted element.
trans-unit.target: jQuery.effects.createPlaceholder() 将创建一个占位符，其显示，位置，尺寸和边距与原始元素相同。占位符作为原始元素的下一个兄弟插入到DOM中。当动画完成后， jQuery.effects.removePlaceholder() 应被用来去除插入的元件。

trans-unit.source: jQuery.effects.define() stores the new effect in jQuery.effects.effect[ name ] and returns the function that was provided as the effect parameter.
trans-unit.target: jQuery.effects.define() 将新效果存储在 jQuery.effects.effect[ name ] 并返回作为 effect 参数提供的函数。

trans-unit.source: options: an object of configuration options
trans-unit.target: options ：配置选项的对象

trans-unit.source: spinner: This uses a class selector as the value. Requires either adding the class manually or initializing the spinner manually. Can be overridden to use input[type=number], but that also requires custom CSS to remove the native number controls.
trans-unit.target: spinner ：这使用类选择器作为值。需要手动添加类或手动初始化微调器。可以重写以使用 input[type=number] ，但这也需要自定义CSS才能删除本地数字控件。

trans-unit.source: ui-accordion-content: The content panels of the accordion. The active content panel will additionally have a ui-accordion-content-active class.
trans-unit.target: ui-accordion-content ：手风琴的内容面板。活动内容面板将另外具有 ui-accordion-content-active 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-accordion-header-icon: Icon elements within each accordion header.
trans-unit.target: ui-accordion-header-icon ：每个手风琴标题中的图标元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-accordion-header: The headers of the accordion. The active header will additionally have a ui-accordion-header-active class, the inactive headers will have a ui-accordion-header-collapsed class. The headers will also have a ui-accordion-icons class if they contain icons.
trans-unit.target: ui-accordion-header ：手风琴的标题。活动标题将另外具有 ui-accordion-header-active 类，非活动标题将具有 ui-accordion-header-collapsed 类。如果标题包含 icons 则标题还将具有 ui-accordion-icons 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-accordion: The outer container of the accordion.
trans-unit.target: ui-accordion ：手风琴的外部容器。

trans-unit.source: ui-autocomplete-input: The input element that the autocomplete widget was instantiated with. While requesting data to display to the user, the ui-autocomplete-loading class is also added to this element.
trans-unit.target: ui-autocomplete-input ：实例化自动完成小部件的输入元素。在请求数据显示给用户时， ui-autocomplete-loading 类也已添加到此元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-autocomplete: The menu used to display matches to the user.
trans-unit.target: ui-autocomplete ：用于显示与用户匹配的菜单。

trans-unit.source: ui-button-icon-space: A separator element between icon and text content of the button. This will only be present if an icon is provided in the icon option and the iconPosition option is set to "beginning" or "end".
trans-unit.target: ui-button-icon-space ：按钮的图标和文本内容之间的分隔符元素。仅当在icon选项中提供了图标并且iconPosition选项设置为 "beginning" 或 "end" ，此选项才会存在。

trans-unit.source: ui-button-icon: The element used to display the button icon. This will only be present if an icon is provided in the icon option.
trans-unit.target: ui-button-icon ：用于显示按钮图标的元素。仅在icon选项中提供了图标的情况下，此选项才会存在。

trans-unit.source: ui-button: The DOM element that represents the button. This element will additionally have the ui-button-icon-only class, depending on the showLabel and icon options.
trans-unit.target: ui-button ：代表按钮的DOM元素。该元素还将具有 ui-button-icon-only 类，具体取决于showLabel和icon选项。

trans-unit.source: ui-buttonset: The outer container of Buttonsets.
trans-unit.target: ui-buttonset ：Buttonset的外部容器。

trans-unit.source: ui-checkboxradio-icon-space: If the icon option is enabled, an extra element with this class as added between the text label and the icon.
trans-unit.target: ui-checkboxradio-icon-space ：如果启用了 icon 选项，则在文本标签和图标之间添加一个带有此类的额外元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-checkboxradio-icon: If the icon option is enabled, the generated icon has this class.
trans-unit.target: ui-checkboxradio-icon ：如果启用了 icon 选项，则生成的图标具有此类。

trans-unit.source: ui-checkboxradio-label: The label associated with the input. If the input is checked, this will also get the ui-checkboxradio-checked class. If the input is of type radio, this will also get the ui-checkboxradio-radio-label class.
trans-unit.target: ui-checkboxradio-label ：与输入关联的标签。如果输入被选中，这还将获得 ui-checkboxradio-checked 类。如果输入的类型为radio，则还将获得 ui-checkboxradio-radio-label 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-checkboxradio: The input of type radio or checkbox. Will be hidden, with its associated label positioned on top.
trans-unit.target: ui-checkboxradio ：单选或复选框类型的输入。将被隐藏，其相关标签位于顶部。

trans-unit.source: ui-controlgroup-item: Each item inside the group.
trans-unit.target: ui-controlgroup-item ：组内的每个项目。

trans-unit.source: ui-controlgroup: The outer container of controlgroups. Depending on the direction option, this element will additionally have the ui-controlgroup-horizontal or ui-controlgroup-vertical classes.
trans-unit.target: ui-controlgroup ：控制组的外部容器。根据方向选项，此元素还将具有 ui-controlgroup-horizontal 或 ui-controlgroup-vertical 类别。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-buttonpane: The buttonpane that is used when the showButtonPanel option is set.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-buttonpane ：设置 showButtonPanel 选项时使用的按钮窗格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-calendar: The table that contains the calendar itself.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-calendar ：包含日历本身的表。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-current-day: The cell containing the selected day.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-current-day ：包含所选日期的单元格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-current: The button used to select today's date.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-current ：用于选择今天的日期的按钮。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-group: Individual pickers within the group. This element will additionally have a ui-datepicker-group-first, ui-datepicker-group-middle, or ui-datepicker-group-last class name depending on its position within the group.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-group ：组内的各个选择器。此元素还将根据其在组中的位置而具有 ui-datepicker-group-first ， ui-datepicker-group-middle 或 ui-datepicker-group-last 类名称。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-header: The container for the datepicker's header.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-header ：日期选择器标头的容器。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-month: The textual display of the month or a <select> element if the changeMonth option is set.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-month ：月份的文本显示，或者如果设置了 changeMonth 选项，则为 <select> 元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-multi: The outermost container of a multiple month datepicker. This element can additionally have a ui-datepicker-multi-2, ui-datepicker-multi-3, or ui-datepicker-multi-4 class name depending on the number of months to display.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-multi ：多个日期选择器的最外面的容器。根据要显示的月份数，此元素还可以具有 ui-datepicker-multi-2 ， ui-datepicker-multi-3 或 ui-datepicker-multi-4 类名称。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-next: The control used to select subsequent months.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-next ：用于选择后续月份的控件。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-other-month: Cells containing days that occur in a month other than the currently selected month.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-other-month ：包含当前日期以外的其他月份的日期的单元格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-prev: The control used to select previous months.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-prev ：用于选择前几个月的控件。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-title: The container for the datepicker's title containing the month and year.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-title ：日期选择器标题的容器，其中包含月份和年份。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-today: The cell containing today's date.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-today ：包含今天日期的单元格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-unselectable: Cells containing days that are not selectable by the user.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-unselectable ：包含用户无法选择的日期的单元格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-week-end: Cells containing weekend days.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-week-end ：包含周末的单元格。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker-year: The textual display of the year or a <select> element if the changeYear option is set.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker-year ：年份的文本显示或 <select> 元素（如果设置了 changeYear 选项）。

trans-unit.source: ui-datepicker: The outer container of the datepicker. If the datepicker is inline, this element will additionally have a ui-datepicker-inline class. If the isRTL option is set, this element will additionally have a class of ui-datepicker-rtl.
trans-unit.target: ui-datepicker ：日期选择器的外部容器。如果datepicker是内联的，则此元素还将具有 ui-datepicker-inline 类。如果设置了 isRTL 选项，则此元素还将具有 ui-datepicker-rtl 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-buttonpane: The pane that contains the dialog's buttons. This will only be present if the buttons option is set.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-buttonpane ：包含对话框按钮的窗格。仅当设置了 buttons 选项时，该选项才会出现。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-buttonset: The container around the buttons themselves.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-buttonset ：按钮本身周围的容器。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-content: The container around the dialog's content. This is also the element the widget was instantiated with.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-content ：对话框内容周围的容器。这也是实例化小部件的元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-title: The container around the textual title of the dialog.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-title ：对话框文本标题周围的容器。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-titlebar-close: The dialog's close button.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-titlebar-close ：对话框的关闭按钮。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog-titlebar: The title bar containing the dialog's title and close button.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog-titlebar ：标题栏，包含对话框的标题和关闭按钮。

trans-unit.source: ui-dialog: The outer container of the dialog. If the draggable option is set, the ui-dialog-dragging class is added during a drag. If the resizable option is set, the ui-dialog-resizing class is added during a resize. If the buttons option is set, the ui-dialog-buttons class is added.
trans-unit.target: ui-dialog ：对话框的外部容器。如果设置了 draggable 选项，则在拖动过程中将添加 ui-dialog-dragging 类。如果设置了 resizable 选项，则在调整大小期间将添加 ui-dialog-resizing 类。如果设置了 buttons 选项，则添加 ui-dialog-buttons 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-draggable-handle: The handle of the draggable, specified using the handle option. By default, the draggable element itself is also the handle.
trans-unit.target: ui-draggable-handle ：可拖动的句柄，使用 handle 选项指定。默认情况下，可拖动元素本身也是句柄。

trans-unit.source: ui-draggable: The draggable element. When the draggable is disabled, the ui-draggable-disabled class is added. While dragging, the ui-draggable-dragging class is added.
trans-unit.target: ui-draggable ：可拖动元素。禁用可拖动时，将添加 ui-draggable-disabled 类。拖动时，将添加 ui-draggable-dragging 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-droppable: The droppable element. When a draggable that can be dropped on this dropppable is activated, the ui-droppable-active class is added. When dragging a draggable over this droppable, the ui-droppable-hover class is added.
trans-unit.target: ui-droppable ：可放置元素。激活可拖放到该可放置对象上的可拖动对象时，将添加 ui-droppable-active 类。当在此可放置对象上拖动可拖动对象时，将添加 ui-droppable-hover 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-menu-divider: Divider elements between menu items.
trans-unit.target: ui-menu-divider ：菜单项之间的分隔元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-menu-icon: The submenu icons set via the icons option.
trans-unit.target: ui-menu-icon ：子菜单图标通过 icons 选项设置。

trans-unit.source: ui-menu-item-wrapper: The wrapper element inside each individual menu item, containting the text content and the icon indicating submenus.
trans-unit.target: ui-menu-item-wrapper ：每个菜单项内的wrapper元素，包含文本内容和指示子菜单的图标。

trans-unit.source: ui-menu-item: The container for individual menu items. This contains the element for the item's text itself as well as the element for submenus.
trans-unit.target: ui-menu-item ：单个菜单项的容器。它包含项目文本本身的元素以及子菜单的元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-menu: The outer container of the menu, as well as any nested submenu. This top-level element will additionally have a ui-menu-icons class if the menu contains icons.
trans-unit.target: ui-menu ：菜单的外部容器以及任何嵌套的子菜单。如果菜单包含图标，则此顶级元素还将另外具有 ui-menu-icons 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-progressbar-overlay: Overlay used to display an animation for indeterminate progressbars.
trans-unit.target: ui-progressbar-overlay ：用于显示不确定进度条的动画的覆盖。

trans-unit.source: ui-progressbar-value: The element that represents the filled portion of the progressbar.
trans-unit.target: ui-progressbar-value ：表示进度条已填充部分的元素。

trans-unit.source: ui-progressbar: The outer container of the progressbar. This element will additionally have a class of ui-progressbar-indeterminate for indeterminate progressbars. For determinate progressbars, the ui-progressbar-complete class is added once the maximum value is reached.
trans-unit.target: ui-progressbar ：进度条的外容器。对于不确定的进度条，此元素还将具有一类 ui-progressbar-indeterminate 。对于确定的进度条，一旦达到最大值，就会添加 ui-progressbar-complete 类。

trans-unit.source: ui-resizable-ghost: When using the ghost option, this class is applied to the ghost helper element.
